text.tspan: Look at this new GNOME branding! It's a letterhead. It would probably not be as
inexpensive to produce as letterheads go, but it's pretty stylin' isn't it? It's hopefully
got the vibrant colors and shapes that broadcast the GNOME brand.
Anyway, I hope you like this letterhead and it meets with your aesthetic approval.
If not, I have failed. In that case, can you buy me a cookie so I feel better?
I look forward to your feedback and potentially a cookie.
